First draft of README file
==========================

==================
To compile library
==================
On Linux :
$cd Build
$./bootstrap
$./configure --prefix=<path to install> --with-libARUpdaterInstall=<path of libARUpdater install>
$make
$make install (if you want to install library)

See example:
./bootstrap
./configure --prefix=/Users/david/FreeFlight3/ARBuildUtils/Targets/Unix/Install
make
make install


